Package com.google.crypto.tink

Class KeysetManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.crypto.tink.KeysetManager
  • public final class KeysetManager
extends Object
    Manages a Keyset proto, with convenience methods that rotate, disable, enable or destroy keys.
